  introLines:
  - That boulder came out of nowhere! Also, you belong in a museum.
  - Fine, you caught me. But you'll never find where I hid the silver idol!
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I swapped a bag of sand for a golden artifact. Apparently,
    the pressure plate didn't care about my math skills. Next thing I know, I'm pancaked
  answerWhatKindOfLife: Exciting, dangerous, and highly illegal. I traveled the world,
    saw ancient ruins, and stole anything that wasn't bolted down
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I 'liberated' cultural artifacts from forgotten temples and
    sold them to wealthy collectors who didn't ask questions
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: Do you have any idea how hard it is to outrun a ancient
    trap in a dusty cave? Of course my clothes are trashed
  answerWhyHaveItem: "A whip wasn't available, so I brought this rusty axe. It\u2019s
    perfect for breaking locks, cutting ropes, and looking intimidating"
